Puggi: What's this fat radish... I mean, what's wrong, little mandora?
Puggi: What happened here?
Mandora: Do~~ Ra~~
Puggi: Ahhh, so it was a rainstorm, huh? No wonder this place is such a mess.
Mandora: Dora...

Mandora: Dora~~~!
Puggi: Alright! Enough with the crying! You'll cramp the main character's style!
Puggi: Plus, crying won't fix your house up, will it?

Puggi: No need to thank me~ This all just comes naturally to the main character.
Puggi: Wahahahaha!
Queendora: To think that Sir Puggi himself would offer his help in rebuilding our home... I'm humbled by the thought!

Queendora: So please, Sir Puggi, accept this gift we have prepared in your honor!
Puggi: Of course~ Although I would gladly keep working, reward or not.
Puggi: No putting down our tools just yet!!
Puggi: We've still much work to do! This house won't build itself!
Mandora: Dora~~~
Queendora: Amazing! Sir Puggi is really something~
Mandora King: Sir Puggi, please accept this reward to thank you for all your help.
Puggi: Yes, yes, of course, my reward~
Mandora King: If it weren't for you, Sir Puggi, I'm afraid...
Puggi: Men! The end is in sight! I can see a beautiful home just on the horizon~!!
Puggi: Steady your heads! This is the final push!!
Mandora: Dora~~!!
Mandora King: Ah, what hard work they're doing...
Mandora King: I just hope they don't overwork themselves! Dora~

Mandora King: Sir Puggi, I speak for the entire kingdom when I say thank you. Thank you for all of your help.

Puggi: And I will extend those words of gratitude to all those players on their phones right now~!
Puggi: They're the ones who really put in the work~♥
Mandora King: Um... What are you talking about, Sir Puggi?

Puggi: Never you mind! 
Now, there's been talk about my reward?
Mandora King: Yes, Sir Puggi, please accept this as a token of our graditude.
Queendora: It simply radiates with our love and appreciation for all of your hard work. We hope you like it.
Puggi: Of course I'll like it~ It's from my fans, after all!
Mandora King: Your... fans?
Puggi: In the future, whenever you run into any trouble, just know you can always count on me to come lend a hand~♥
Mandora King: Oh my, Sir Puggi is just too generous!
Queendora: All hail Sir Puggi!
Mandora: Dora~Dora~~~
